#

Lemon Garlic Butter Shrimp with Broccoli Rice

$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

High-ProteinLow-CarbGluten-Free

Tags:

SeafoodQuick MealHealthy

Description

A quick and delicious shrimp dish sautéed in lemon garlic butter, served with a healthy broccoli rice.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp: 1 lb
  • Broccoli florets: 2 cups
  • Garlic: 4 cloves
  • Butter: 3 tbsp
  • Lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • Olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Chili flakes: optional
